{"tid":535591,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"又想入閘？黃成智突開記招講「新界東補選事宜」","createTime":"2018-01-21T04:42:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-21T09:13:37.000Z","uid":20933,"like":2,"dislike":25,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"7082753eb49e3987b5aa753ecf4dc1e8f1028f4b","tid":535591,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-21T04:42:30.000Z","msg":"前立法會議員、上屆於新東立法會敗選的黃成智，今早發放題為【選擇理性的勇氣】採訪通知，稱今天會召開記者會「就新界東補選事宜作出公佈」。<br />\n<br />\n《蘋果》曾致電黃成智欲了解是否宣佈參選，電話無人接聽；其助理則只重申黃有補選事宜宣佈。<br />\n<br />\n新民主同盟范國威早前勝出民主派初選，會代表民主派於新東出戰；工聯會鄧家彪則代表建制派上陣。"},{"pid":"72ab0048ebb178275ea9e1d747b512342ba6ab78","tid":535591,"uid":39800,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-21T04:43:43.000Z","msg":"群魔亂舞<br />\n個位國師㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca98e2791c5874c69b01f8495f228e9c9b892702","tid":535591,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"quote":{"pid":"72ab0048ebb178275ea9e1d747b512342ba6ab78","tid":535591,"uid":39800,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-21T04:43:43.000Z","msg":"群魔亂舞<br />\n個位國師㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-21T04:48:22.000Z","msg":"政治倫理係畀國師<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"782ca1498a3b5295ffcb22ee3dc9aa38d6f732b2","tid":535591,"uid":13257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-21T04:50:58.000Z","msg":"個個見新東係泛民票倉，就想衝入黎分杯羹。但新東d人唔係白痴架。"},{"pid":"633d06913fbb4089f154032e2017b811e373c459","tid":535591,"uid":62815,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-21T04:55:40.000Z","msg":"中間超人又出動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fad5319158316f2d0c0f20a14c878da0bc1525a9","tid":535591,"uid":44358,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"ca98e2791c5874c69b01f8495f228e9c9b892702","tid":535591,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"quote":{"pid":"72ab0048ebb178275ea9e1